@Node "INTR" "Introduction"

@{b}INTRODUCTION@{ub}

«05R/W» is the manager and editor of the KORG 05R/W synthetizer module,
providing a simple and convenient manner for creating programs,
combinations and drumkits. Programs and combination can be tested directly
from your amiga keyboard in real time. Also provided are gfx display for
some program parameters (VDA EG, VDF EG, Pitch EG). Have fun!!

@{b}Main features includes@{ub}
 - nice and intuitive layout thanks to MUI
 - "Combination" manager, import/export and load/save bank or combination
 - "Comination" editor with real time test
 - "Program" manager, import/export and load/save bank or program
 - "Program" editor, with real time test and gfx displays for EGs
 - "Drum Kit" editor, to create your own drumkits
 - "Virtual MIDI Keyboard", with 2 octaves, pitch, modulation and controllers

@EndNode

@Node "REQU" "Requirements"

@{b}REQUIREMENTS@{ub}

@{b}Software@{ub}
 - Kickstart 2.0 or higher
 - Workbench 2.1 or higher
 - @{"MUI 3.1" link "MUI3"} or higher (not provided -> util/libs)
 - midi.library version 7.0 or higher.

@{b}Hardware@{ub}
 - a MIDI-Interface could be helpful
 - KORG 05R/W module might also be quite useful...
   (X5 and X5DR should work as well too, but were not tested).

@EndNode

@Node "REGI" "Registration"

@{b}REGISTRATION@{ub}

«05R/W» is shareware, the fee is cheap enough for you to consider
registering, in comparison with the amount of time and effort involved
in the production of this software.

The unregistered version of «05R/W» pops up the about requester
sometimes to remind you to register and some capabilities are disabled.

Registered users will receive the latest public release of «05R/W», and
their personalized "keyfile", which disable the annoying requester and
limitations.  This keyfile will work with all future release of «05R/W»,
and no other charges will be asked for updates.  The keyfile must not be
redistibuted, nor copied on another computer than yours in any way.  I
will also try, if possible, to help registered users in data convertion
coming from other account manager, see registration form.

«05R/W» registration amount is (cash only please):

   80 FF (or eq. DM, Ł, US$) - to receive via E-Mail
  100 FF (or eq. DM, Ł, US$) - to receive on 3,5" DD via Slow Mail

The fastest, cheapest and easiest way to register is to put cash money
together with the filled registration form into a letter (take care of
hidding cash in your registration form for secure reason) and send the
all to:

   Maxime Doyen
   A2/12 rés. Planche Epinoy
   Avenue de Flandres
   59170 Croix
   France

@EndNode

