 - Written an install script.
 - Keyfile was changed.
 - Some correction in documentations, form and readme, especially for
   e-mail addresses 'nornet' was in fact 'nordnet'.
 - Documentation was partially re-written.


Version 1.0 (25-Sep-97)
-----------------------
